Zero trust access, real‑time control

Enforce per-app VPN access with dynamic policies and real-time identity/device checks—reducing risk, stopping insider threats, and supporting regulatory compliance.

Work anywhere, securely

Designed for roaming teams, Connect Secure gives you cost-effective, secure access from any device — empowering IT and enabling agile productivity beyond traditional office boundaries.

Future‑proof integration, seamless control

Connect Secure integrates with your existing security stack — maintaining consistent policies, unified visibility and smooth workflows as infrastructure evolves — no rip-and-replace required.

Features and capabilities

Enterprise‑ready access. Built on zero trust.

Single unified client

Reduce management complexity with only one client for remote and on-site access. 

Easy integration

Directory Services, Identity Services, EMM/MDM, SIEM, NGFWs. 

Dynamic, adaptive multi-factor authentication

Biometric authentication, TOTP, SAML 2.0, PKI, IAM and digital certificates. 

Stateful endpoint compliance

Ensure that all devices comply with security requirements before connecting. 

Single sign-on

Simple, secure and streamlined access to on-premises and cloud-based resources. 

Zero-Trust connections

Protect data-in-motion with on-demand, per-application and always-on VPN options. 

Data center and multi-cloud

Access that’s easy, compliant and multi-cloud ready. 

Centralized management and visibility
